Package ca.cgjennings.ui.textedit

Annotation Interface NoAutoRepeat

@Retention(RUNTIME) @Target(TYPE) public @interface NoAutoRepeat
An annotation that can be applied to an editor command's ActionListener to indicate that it will take responsibility for repetition. When this annotation is present, and the editor is repeating a command, the InputHandler will not automatically repeat the command.
Since:
3.0
See Also:
EditorCommands.REPEAT, InputHandler.getRepeatCount()
